{
  "stem": "1511.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I sit on-- with the religious one, I sit on the top with the women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went up to to daven-- he davened special with all these melodies when we were davening in Europe and our shtiebel when we had.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we helped and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never in my life for happiness, and the way he was davning, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we took ourselves with the hands, and we went and told stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I want to know-- I want to know, how did you survive?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But a little bit, I find out in Bratslav, when I came to Bratslav, and I was with them awhile, and they told me how they survived.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When the war started, my father wasn't there, but my mother was there and all the kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They made under a chicken little house, what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A bunker.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were sitting there day and night, but when it came Yom Kippur, after Yom Kippur, they were sitting, and they had nothing to eat, and the house was just a few shacks away.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was my auntie with her kids too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chanale is the doctor's mother there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some other people that I don't know-- neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, and between that, when the war started, and they were with Hitler, my sister, Chavcha, she had a girlfriend, and her name was Salka in Polish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She took my whole family-- about 60 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had them for six weeks in-- hidden by her in another-- in a little-- in a farm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember the place where that was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later, it got bad, and they had to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that was with them when they were hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
